name: Metallic Display Scroll
description: Loki slipped a hand in his jacket. "You might find some of my surveillance video interesting." He withdrew a metallic scroll and offered it to Philips. She took the metallic scroll and pulled the twin tubes apart to reveal a glossy, flexible video screen already glowing with electrical energy From Freedom by Daniel Suarez. Published by Dutton in 2010.
